Stats

The things that predicts the percentage of FSM students in a school are the percentage of FSM students in a LA and the progress 8 score of school. The higher the progress 8 (P8MEA), the lower the percentage of FSM students in a school:

Sch FSM % ~ Gender + LA FSM % + Region FSM % + Progress 8
